Segment 1 Opportunities: Senior Management

Minimize failures of projects due to poor communication  

Minimize ambiguity of the vision and strategy on projects

Minimize doubts over cost vs benefits of a project

Minimize risk of project failure with a ‘next best option’ 

Communication and Persuasion:
Senior Management, Business Users and Internal Team

Segment 2 Opportunities: Business users

Minimize the lack of usefulness of software 

Minimize wasted time with updates and direction through Agile methodology.

Minimize the chance that requirements can be misunderstood 


Segment 3 Opportunities: Internal Team

Minimize the effort required to develop a new software feature

Minimize the lack of communication with a process for messaging another team member 

Minimize lack of understanding of protein science when writing code for the domain





